{"tid":2084211,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實每次都唔想出嚟， 但一諗到手足係出面奮戰緊， 就提醒咗我一定要出嚟","createTime":"2020-06-29T06:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-29T12:41:33.000Z","uid":353200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a3f04867204c962d90824eb6f90c1427f01fbc51","tid":2084211,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:47:41.000Z","msg":"又熱又可能畀人拉風險又高， 但只要諗起手足嘅努力， 同埋諗起身邊會出嚟幫手嘅朋友， 我就每次都會出嚟希望可以盡一分綿力，。<br />\n<br />\n唔好話要光復香港話， 唔係話要民主自由， 但如果你想保護你身邊嘅朋友， 唔想增加佢哋畀人拉嘅風險， 希望大家可以挺身而出保護身邊嘅人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家記得喺ig同facebook都要share文書提醒其他朋友出嚟<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2020/06/29/144725_e7df02ac83f9f376f3678bb7d724f619.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2020%2F06%2F29%2F144725_e7df02ac83f9f376f3678bb7d724f619.JPG&h=3f8649da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【#71遊行 堅持五大訴求　反抗國安惡法】<br />\n<br />\n日期｜2020 年 7 月 1 日 星期三<br />\n集合地點｜維園集合<br />\n集合時間｜2PM<br />\n起步時間｜3PM<br />\n遊行終點｜金鐘添美道<br />\n*遊行正申請不反對通知書<br />\n<br />\n#71Rally<br />\nFIVE DEMANDS, NOT ONE LESS<br />\nRESIST NATIONAL SECURITY LAW<br />\n<br />\nDate｜1st July 2020, Wednesday<br />\nStarting Point｜Victoria Park<br />\nAssemble｜2PM<br />\nStart｜3PM<br />\nEnd Point｜Tim Mei Avenue, Admiralty<br />\n*Letter of No Objection Pending<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n【民陣 TG】 <a href=\"http://t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FCivilHumanRightsFront&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=cc1acfd5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/CivilHumanRightsFront</a><br />\n【民陣 Twitter】 <a href=\"http://twitter.com/chrf_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fchrf_hk&d=Q4XCoHks6IcJcnuFSE4RTYT2PPn%2Ft%2FQrHStoP3Eljfw%3D&h=9caf2732\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">twitter.com/chrf_hk</a><br />\n【民陣 IG】 chrf_hk<br />\n<br />\n民陣被捕法律支援熱線：6549 9452<br />\nWhatsapp / SMS / Telegram<br />\n<br />\n請提供資料：（＊必要）<br />\n<br />\n1. 被捕地點<br />\n2. 中文全名＊<br />\n3. 英文全名<br />\n4. 身份證號碼<br />\n5. 性別、年齡<br />\n6. 當事人電話<br />\n7. 所在警署<br />\n8. 緊急聯絡人電話＊<br />\n9. 報料人電話＊（若與緊急聯絡人不同）<br />\n10. 其他詳情（如有）"},{"pid":"c0626b0adc0417d5886a793e1b1616dab90c2bad","tid":2084211,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你哋班連登仔， 喺連登圍爐洗版有撚用？</span><br />\n<br />\n我要見到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IG Facebook</span>  各大社交平台<br />\n都要見到呢幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7月1 維園見</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"7e47fd7196bc1a0248ad4e9ecfc5601c1eeb5f1d","tid":2084211,"uid":353200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0626b0adc0417d5886a793e1b1616dab90c2bad","tid":2084211,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:47:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">你哋班連登仔， 喺連登圍爐洗版有撚用？</span><br />\n<br />\n我要見到<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">IG Facebook</span>  各大社交平台<br />\n都要見到呢幾隻字<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>7月1 維園見</strong></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"我ig就見到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望其他人都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82d29c24ba06b8983924a7b3358e0d99fb2c91ac","tid":2084211,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif